Call TEXTE(43545,GBOUT11) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(15597,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_CLIENT(zc) From W1CRMLCM
Onkey 139 Titled GBOUT11 Call B11_CLIENT(zc) From W1CRMLCM
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CLIENT(zc) From W1CRMLCM
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CLIENT(zc) From W1CRMLCM
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_CLIENT(zc) From W1CRMLCM
